  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Active-controlled, Multicenter Study to Compare the Effect of 24 Weeks Treatment With a Fixed Combination Therapy of Vildagliptin and Metformin to the Individual Monotherapy Components in Drug Naive Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
