  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female (non-fertile or of childbearing potential using a medically approved
             birth control method) patients with type 2 diabetes

          -  Diagnosis of T2DM for at least 4 weeks prior to study entry

          -  Age 18 - 78 years inclusive

          -  Body mass index (BMI) of 22 - 40 kg/m2

          -  HbA1c: 7.5 - 11% inclusive

          -  FPG &lt;270 mg/dL (15 mmol/L)

        Exclusion Criteria

          -  Pregnant or lactating female

          -  A history of type 1 diabetes

          -  Evidence of significant diabetic complications

          -  Other protocol-defined inclusion/exclusion criteria may apply
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
